Entries.default: "This place looks a lot like the old Engwithan ruins back home but... like they were just built."
"These structures are of Engwithan make, but they look to be new. Strange."
"This place has eyes that pry through falsehood, I say. Someone is watching our every step."
"Adra... arches... inlaid copper. Ruins of Engwith, I suspect. Wait, who's that?"
"Ymir'd give his left nut to see this."
"I am no stranger to Engwithan ruins, but all of this looks very new."
"Cold stone, like a tomb. Maybe we do not disturb what lingers here."
